              "type": "heading2",
              "text": "When Fragrance Becomes Art",
              "spans": []
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "At Abu Dhabi Art Fair, Hind Al-Oud revealed Ahojas through an immersive installation that transformed fragrance into art. Designed as a sculptural, multi-sensory environment, the space invited visitors to think, feel, and create, positioning perfume as both an emotional journey and a contemporary artwork.",
              "spans": []
            }
